issue.title: script for launching SQL database and then launching server
issue.body: Also, need to look into a way to disabling the apollo server default frontend for the backend.

issue.title: save and load the database from a file
issue.body:
Right now, the existing server does not load or save data from a file. 

Instead, it creates and launches the database (empty) and populates it with the hardcoded buildings, and a few bathrooms.

The database should instead load and save its state to a file upon launch and end, accordingly.
